{
  "texts": [
    "This research investigates several models for CRC classification which are evaluated using several experiments.",
    "Experiment I investigates end-to-end classification using three CNNs which are AlexNet, ResNet50, and DenseNet201 with two training-testing ratios to overcome overfitting.",
    "The training-testing ratios are 70-30 and 60-40.",
    "In Experiment II, features are extracted from each network and passed to two the SVM and ESD classifiers.",
    "Experiment III evaluates the use of the DCT for feature reduction."
  ]
}